'''阿塔巴德湖'''（Attabad Lake，{{lang-ur|عطا آباد جھیل}}），又稱戈賈爾湖（Gojal Lake），位于[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[吉尔吉特-巴尔蒂斯坦省|吉尔吉特-巴尔蒂斯坦省]]的[[罕萨河谷|罕萨河谷]]。2010年，大型的山体滑坡阻塞了河流，經過幾個月的蓄水後形成了一個堰塞湖-阿塔巴德湖<ref>{{citation|title=Gojal Lake Hazard|date=21 July 2015|url=http://pamirtimes.net/tag/gojal-lake-hazard/|work=Pamir Times|location=Islamabad|accessdate=2021-03-31|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202153644/https://pamirtimes.net/tag/gojal-lake-hazard/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，湖泊绵延30公里(19英里)，有120米(400英尺)深。<ref name="fourworlds_HiMaT_2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.fourworlds.ca/documents/ASecondGreenRevolution.pdf|title=Needed: a second green revolution in Hunza|accessdate=26 November 2015|date=May 2013|publisher=HiMaT|pages=4|author1=Michael Bopp|author2=Judie Bopp|archive-date=2015-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127021618/http://www.fourworlds.ca/documents/ASecondGreenRevolution.pdf|dead-url=no}} Karakorum Area Development Organization (KADO), Aliabad</ref><ref>[https://www.serenahotels.com/serenahunza/阿塔巴德湖和博利斯湖-,experiences_viewItem_1951-zh.html “阿塔巴德湖和博利斯湖”] Serena Hotel Hunza</ref>阿塔巴德湖自此之後成为吉尔吉特-巴尔蒂斯坦最受欢迎的旅游景点之一。<ref>[http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-10/25/c_139465402.htm “Friendship highway leads Pakistan's Hunza to prosperity as tourism industry booms”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-10/25/c_139465402.htm |date=20201101032158 }} Xinhua Net [25-10-2020]</ref>

